This PHP application implements a listener service for a PayPal invoked
Instant Payment Notification (IPN).

As defined by the following PayPal documents.

https://www.x.com/developers/paypal/documentation-tools/ipn/integration-guide/IPNIntro
https://www.x.com/developers/PayPal/documentation-tools/code-sample/216623

This application takes care to preserve the contents of the original IPN
message, and also optionally parse out fields of interest.
